      <arrangement id="aspace_4bf88ee88174df00311d20c17a4ffa9f">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The materials are arranged by accession.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_193fe9890ba2f6db66272cbd0969b22b">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of 16 mm films and VHS videotapes documenting men's crew races and training at Yale.</p>
         <p>There is also film of the Yale-Harvard boat races, circa 1930, with film of the 1930 Yale-Army football game donated by John Kieffer (see RU 971, Accession 2013-A-082).</p>  
      </scopecontent>
